{"componentChunkName":"component---src-page-post-tsx","path":"/learn-about-asynchronous-communication-why-phone-is-bad-and-chat-is-good","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Markus Tacker","tagLine":"Software Crafter","description":"Software Crafter building üå©Ô∏è cloud-based cellular IoT solutions at Nordic Semiconductor.‚Äã\n\t\tMentor. Speaker. ‚ÄãConference & Community builder. Camper. üèïÔ∏è üöê","gitHubUrl":"https://github.com/coderbyheart/coderbyheart.com.git","siteUrl":"https://coderbyheart.com","twitter":"@coderbyheart","defaultCard":"https://images.ctfassets.net/bncv3c2gt878/3Jk4P6nFPNzaz1gsguktk8/350b7e4ddb2c7d86416243d9902920e2/social-card-default-2020.png"}}},"pageContext":{"page":{"id":"d9a8b9e7-7bcd-55f7-ae66-890bbf1b0f7c","name":"learn-about-asynchronous-communication-why-phone-is-bad-and-chat-is-good","relativeDirectory":"post","relativePath":"post/learn-about-asynchronous-communication-why-phone-is-bad-and-chat-is-good.md","remark":{"htmlAst":{"children":[{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"This post tries to explain the rationale behind one of\n"},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"my recent tweets"}],"tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://twitter.com/coderbyheart/status/612577493594284032","target":"_blank","rel":["nofollow","noreferrer"]},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":":"}],"tagName":"p","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"Everyone will work better if all understand the difference between sync and\nasync communication: "},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"Phone is bad, Chat is good."}],"tagName":"strong","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":" >\n"},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"#futureofwork"}],"tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://twitter.com/hashtag/futureofwork?src=hash","target":"_blank","rel":["nofollow","noreferrer"]},"type":"element"}],"tagName":"p","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"}],"tagName":"blockquote","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"You can maximize your work output if you can use your work time in a way the\nsuits your habits best. The more your work requires your undivided attention,\nwhich is true especially for creative and innovative work, the more your mind\nwill submerge into something called "},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"flow"}],"tagName":"em","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":", a state of mind that shuts out all\nexterior disturbances and focuses on the one task at hand. I call this the core\nworking time, that part of the day which is dedicated to the work that you are\nbest doing at."}],"tagName":"p","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[{"children":[{"children":[],"tagName":"path","properties":{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"},"type":"element"}],"tagName":"svg","properties":{"ariaHidden":"true","focusable":"false","height":"16","version":"1.1","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","width":"16"},"type":"element"}],"tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#flow-needs-an-environment-of-self-determination-and-independence-to-happen","ariaLabel":"flow needs an environment of self determination and independence to happen permalink","className":["anchor","before"]},"type":"element"},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"flow"}],"tagName":"em","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":" needs an environment of self-determination and independence to happen"}],"tagName":"h2","properties":{"id":"flow-needs-an-environment-of-self-determination-and-independence-to-happen","style":"position:relative;"},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"There are two important things to consider:"},{"children":[],"tagName":"br","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"Flow can't be switched on"}],"tagName":"em","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":" just like that, you need the environment and the\npersonal condition to activate it. It's a very individual condition that is\nentirely up to you and can't be determined by putting you in a cubicle from 9 to\n5 with motivational posters around. You are in charge of picking the time of a\nday and the location that provide the best conditions for you to be able to do\n"},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"your best work possible"}],"tagName":"em","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"."},{"children":[],"tagName":"br","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"It takes time"}],"tagName":"em","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":" for your brain to enter a higher state of concentration that\nenables you to "},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"see"}],"tagName":"em","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":" all the factors of a problem and "},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"understand"}],"tagName":"em","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":" patterns that\nemerge-only then will you be able to find a good solution to a given problem.\nIt's a matter of hours and not minutes until you can focus all your senses on a\nproblem."}],"tagName":"p","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"If you work at an organization where innovation and creativity is key to your\norganization's success you want everyone to reach their "},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"flow"}],"tagName":"em","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":" at least once a\nday. But as I pointed out before, it can't be planned nor can it be mandated.\n"},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"flow"}],"tagName":"em","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":" needs an environment of self-determination and independence to happen."}],"tagName":"p","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[{"children":[{"children":[],"tagName":"path","properties":{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"},"type":"element"}],"tagName":"svg","properties":{"ariaHidden":"true","focusable":"false","height":"16","version":"1.1","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","width":"16"},"type":"element"}],"tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#phone-calls-are-poison-in-these-environment","ariaLabel":"phone calls are poison in these environment permalink","className":["anchor","before"]},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"Phone calls are poison in these environment"}],"tagName":"h2","properties":{"id":"phone-calls-are-poison-in-these-environment","style":"position:relative;"},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"Every time you pick up your phone to call a colleague you have a very high\nprobability of disturbing their flow and yanking them out of their core working\ntime. Why is that? You will force their mind to step out of its current\nengagement and refocus on the question you need to have answered. Is your\nproblem that important? I'd argued that it is not for most of the time. The same\nis true for walking up to someone's desk without invitation."}],"tagName":"p","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"I'm an advocate of asynchronous communication, like chat, because it puts\nestablishes a buffer in the communication that enables every participant to\ncommunication "},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"in their own time"}],"tagName":"em","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":". They can decide when to read chat messages\nbecause they can turn of notification and find the time that fits them to answer\nquestions there."}],"tagName":"p","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"There is nothing wrong with using phone-calls or video-chats for "},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"planned\nmeetings"}],"tagName":"strong","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":". It's essential for the wellbeing of an organization to hear your\ncolleagues voices and synchronous communication should be your choice for all\nyour recurring meetings like the daily, jour fixes or other sync-up style\nmeetings."}],"tagName":"p","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"So it's not the technology that is bad but the implications they bear: phone\ncalls are expected to be answered immediately, that puts some pressure on the\nreceiver. They are not bad per-se because the bandwidth depending on the topic\ncan be higher compared to chat or email."}],"tagName":"p","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[{"children":[{"children":[],"tagName":"path","properties":{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"},"type":"element"}],"tagName":"svg","properties":{"ariaHidden":"true","focusable":"false","height":"16","version":"1.1","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","width":"16"},"type":"element"}],"tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#make-an-escalation-plan-for-communication","ariaLabel":"make an escalation plan for communication permalink","className":["anchor","before"]},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"Make an escalation plan for communication"}],"tagName":"h2","properties":{"id":"make-an-escalation-plan-for-communication","style":"position:relative;"},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"Phone calls might be an easy to use tool for the individual but bear a very\nunbalanced cost for the team. It shouldn't be your first choice of communication\nwith your team."}],"tagName":"p","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"Communication in a team needs to be well defined and agreed on organization\nwide. I propose that chat should be the default way of communication internally.\nYou can replace email with a chat system that allows for private, topic based,\nand general messaging. Your project management tool is the place to assign work\nitems. Email should be an interface only to clients and external contacts."}],"tagName":"p","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"That leaves phone-calls for emergency situations. And you should handle them\nlike this. If you pick up the phone to call someone it should be an emergency.\nYou also should know which kind of problem qualifies for an emergency and which\nare better added to the bug tracker."}],"tagName":"p","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"If you are on the receiving end of a phone-call and it's not an emergency you\nshould know about the effect of immediately taking care of the issue. If you are\nin a state of focus just ask the caller to let you call them back so you can\nfinish your current thought or bring your current work item to a state that\nenables you to easily pick it up later. Give them a time frame and essentially\n"},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"schedule"}],"tagName":"em","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":" a call with them."}],"tagName":"p","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[{"children":[{"children":[],"tagName":"path","properties":{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"},"type":"element"}],"tagName":"svg","properties":{"ariaHidden":"true","focusable":"false","height":"16","version":"1.1","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","width":"16"},"type":"element"}],"tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#synchronous-communication-is-expensive","ariaLabel":"synchronous communication is expensive permalink","className":["anchor","before"]},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"Synchronous communication is expensive"}],"tagName":"h2","properties":{"id":"synchronous-communication-is-expensive","style":"position:relative;"},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"‚Ä¶ is the gist of this post. Separating myself voluntarily from my team by\nworking out of a "},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"coworking space"}],"tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"http://www.die-zentrale-ffm.de/en/","target":"_blank","rel":["nofollow","noreferrer"]},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":" at least\n3 days a week and reducing "},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"unplanned"}],"tagName":"em","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":" phone calls to a minimum is important for\nmy personal happiness at work. I even try to cluster meetings around two days a\nweek so I have the other three days for work that feels more productive to\nme-like coding."}],"tagName":"p","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"I hope you have enough reasons to make your organization default to asynchronous\ncommunication if you have the power to do so."}],"tagName":"p","properties":{},"type":"element"}],"type":"root","data":{"quirksMode":false}},"frontmatter":{"title":"Learn about asynchronous communication: why phone is bad and chat is good","subtitle":null,"noheadline":null,"date":"2015-06-28T11:30:00.000Z","abstract":"This post tries to explain the rationale behind one of my recent tweets: Phone is bad, Chat is good.","lang":null},"headings":[{"id":"flow-needs-an-environment-of-self-determination-and-independence-to-happen","d